
This is the Perl distribution Sub-CharacterProperties.

## Installation

Sub-CharacterProperties installation is straightforward.
If your CPAN shell is set up, you should just be able to do

    % cpan Sub::CharacterProperties

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

## Documentation

Sub-CharacterProperties documentation is available as in POD.
So you can do:

    % perldoc Sub::CharacterProperties

to read the documentation with your favorite pager.
